Bank credit and capital during 1st half of 2020

Configuration of the query to Bloomberg

All the monetary information throughout the script is downloaded in millions od USD. The best options are either “USD” or “EUR”.

The variables below are the fields to be retrieved from Bloomberg for each bank:

Bank variables
IS_PROV_FOR_LOAN_LOSS
BS_TOT_LOAN
BS_TOT_ASSET
BS_LOAN_MTG
BS_RSRV_LOAN_LOSS
IS_OPER_INC
EARN_FOR_COMMON
BS_CUSTOMER_DEPOSITS
BS_LEV_RATIO_TO_TANG_CAP
BS_TIER1_COM_EQUITY_RATIO
BS_TIER1_CAP_RATIO
BS_TOT_CAP_TO_RISK_BASE_CAP
BS_RISK_WEIGHTED_ASSETS
